Chanto boku wa aruite kita kana
Futo tachi tomatte furikaettara
Kono basho e to tsuduku ashiato
Mujaki sugita yume mo itsuka no namida mo
Kitto kyou kono ni hi no tabidachi no tame ni woh ...
